<div type="definition">
<p>RELATION in which MANY HUMANS, FEATURES OR THINGS EXIST TOGETHER OR INTERACT.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current general term for a constellation or situation of any kind is shì 勢.</p>
<p>2. Zhuàng 狀 and xíng 形 can be used to emphasise the external appearance created by a situation.</p>
<p>3. Shì 事 focusses on the factual sequence of events that create a shì 勢.</p>
<p>4. Dì 地 sometimes comes to be used for a stage of a development.</p>
        </div>
